rolled via backend. however they might want to use owncloud with project partners from other organizations. in this case, we make them group admins and let them do what they must do; i.e. create (non-ldap) accounts, assign quotas etc.\r\n\r\nif one of these accounts \"misbehaves\" or what not, i need to be able to disable it (pun intended) without deleting it.\r\n\r\n<rant>\r\nbtw, this scenario also gives rise to other related feature requests that no-one seems to take seriously, such as:\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1347 (10 months ago)\r\n* https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3358 (7 months ago)\r\n* https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4125 (4 months ago)\r\n* https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3362 (7 months ago; took 5 months even to cc: it to a developer)\r\n\r\n</rant>"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/29457147","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/809#issuecomment-29457147","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/809","id":29457147,"user":{"login":"deepdiver1975","id":1005065,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/bdba071ed68da9ce8edae53c364902ef?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f67e101ad9531b7d25697b76e503e062e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"bdba071ed68da9ce8edae53c364902ef","url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975","html_url":"https://github.com/deepdiver1975","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/events{/priva